        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The &amp;quot;Chief Ministers’ Education Assistance Scheme (CMEAS)&amp;quot; was launched by the Education Department, Government of Sikkim. The objective of scheme is to provide financial assistance to students from economically weaker sections, marginalized communities and specially-abled students. Under this scheme, students receive financial aid for pursuing education within the state, outside the state, abroad, and in registered coaching institutions.\n> ***Scheme Implementation:***\n\n\n- The scheme is implemented by the Chief Minister’s Office (CMO), Sikkim, with a dedicated nodal officer for verification, approval, and fund disbursement.\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "> **Nature of Assistance**\n\n**Under the CMEAS, students shall be eligible for the following assistance:**\n**(i) Within State:**\n**SI.No.****Course****Type of Institution****Amount (in ₹) (per month/annum)**1Undergraduates/Diploma and EquivalentGovernment &amp;amp;amp;amp; PrivateUpto ₹5,000/- PM2Professional/Technical- Undergraduate &amp;amp;amp;amp; EquivalentGovernment Upto ₹5,000/- PM3Post Graduate &amp;amp;amp;amp; EquivalentGovernment &amp;amp;amp;amp; PrivateUpto ₹7,000/- PM4Professional/Technical - Postgraduate &amp;amp;amp;amp; EquivalentGovernmentUpto ₹7,000/- PM5PhD &amp;amp;amp;amp; aboveGovernment &amp;amp;amp;amp; PrivateUpto ₹10,000/- PM6Professional/Technical - Undergraduate &amp;amp;amp;amp; EquivalentPrivateUpto ₹1,50,000/- PA7Professional/Technical - Postgraduate &amp;amp;amp;amp; EquivalentPrivateUpto ₹2,00,000/- PA**(ii) Outside State within Country:**\n**SI.No.****Course****Type of Institution****Amount (in ₹) (per month/annum)**1Undergraduates/Diploma and EquivalentGovernment &amp;amp;amp;amp; PrivateUpto ₹7,000/- PM2Professional/Technical- Undergraduate &amp;amp;amp;amp; EquivalentGovernment Upto ₹7,000/- PM3Post Graduate &amp;amp;amp;amp; EquivalentGovernment &amp;amp;amp;amp; PrivateUpto ₹9,000/- PM4Professional/Technical - Postgraduate &amp;amp;amp;amp; EquivalentGovernmentUpto ₹9,000/- PM5PhD &amp;amp;amp;amp; aboveGovernment &amp;amp;amp;amp; PrivateUpto ₹12,000/- PM6Professional/Technical - Undergraduate &amp;amp;amp;amp; EquivalentPrivateUpto ₹2,00,000/- PA7Professional/Technical - Postgraduate &amp;amp;amp;amp; EquivalentPrivateUpto ₹2,50,000/- PA**(iii) Studying Abroad: Upto ₹5,00,000/- PA**\n**(iv) Studying in Coaching Centre: Upto ₹1,50,000/- PA**\n> **Note:**\n\nThe quantum of financial assistance shall be determined based on the student’s financial need and availability of funds.\n",
