                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The \"Chief Ministers’ Education Assistance Scheme (CMEAS)\" was launched by the Education Department, Government of Sikkim. The objective of scheme is to provide financial assistance to students from economically weaker sections, marginalized communities and specially-abled students. Under this scheme, students receive financial aid for pursuing education within the state, outside the state, abroad, and in registered coaching institutions."
