      "applicationProcess": [
        {
          "mode": "Offline",
          "process": [
            {
              "type": "block_quote",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Application Process:",
                  "bold": true
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "align_justify",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "bold": true,
                      "text": "Step 1: "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The interested applicant should visit (during office hours) the designated cell in the Chief Minister’s Office, Tashiling  Secretariat, Gangtok and request a hard copy of the prescribed format of the application form from the staff exclusively entrusted to issue and collect filled-in applications."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step 2:",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " In the application form, fill in all the mandatory fields, and attach copies of all the mandatory documents (self-attested, if required)."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step 3:",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " Submit the duly filled and signed application form along with the documents to the Chief Minister’s Office, Tashiling  Secretariat, Gangtok."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "block_quote",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Post Application Process:",
                      "bold": true
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "bold": true,
                      "text": "Step 1: "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The application will be reviewed and verified through an official procedure."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "bold": true,
                      "text": "Step 2: "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "A nodal officer appointed by the CMO will oversee eligibility, approval, fund disbursement, and record-keeping."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "bold": true,
                      "text": "Step 3: "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Upon approval, financial assistance will be disbursed directly to the applicant’s bank account."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "block_quote",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Application Renewal  Process:",
                      "bold": true
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "bold": true,
                      "text": "The financial assistance granted under this scheme may be renewed annually until the completion of the student’s course of study, subject to the following conditions:"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "bold": true,
                      "text": "Step 1: "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The student must remain enrolled in the educational institution during the period of renewal."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "bold": true,
                      "text": "Step 2: "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The student must have passed and cleared all prescribed courses (semester/annual) in the enrolled academic programme."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "bold": true,
                      "text": "Step 3: "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The student must continue to meet the eligibility criteria."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "bold": true,
                      "text": "Step 4: "
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The scholarship from other sources will be reviewed while verifying the applications and the eligibility will be considered accordingly."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "process_md": "> **Application Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** The interested applicant should visit (during office hours) the designated cell in the Chief Minister’s Office, Tashiling  Secretariat, Gangtok and request a hard copy of the prescribed format of the application form from the staff exclusively entrusted to issue and collect filled-in applications.\n**Step 2:** In the application form, fill in all the mandatory fields, and attach copies of all the mandatory documents (self-attested, if required).\n**Step 3:** Submit the duly filled and signed application form along with the documents to the Chief Minister’s Office, Tashiling  Secretariat, Gangtok.\n&gt; **Post Application Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** The application will be reviewed and verified through an official procedure.\n**Step 2:** A nodal officer appointed by the CMO will oversee eligibility, approval, fund disbursement, and record-keeping.\n**Step 3:** Upon approval, financial assistance will be disbursed directly to the applicant’s bank account.\n&gt; **Application Renewal  Process:**\n\n**The financial assistance granted under this scheme may be renewed annually until the completion of the student’s course of study, subject to the following conditions:**\n**Step 1:** The student must remain enrolled in the educational institution during the period of renewal.\n**Step 2:** The student must have passed and cleared all prescribed courses (semester/annual) in the enrolled academic programme.\n**Step 3:** The student must continue to meet the eligibility criteria.\n**Step 4:** The scholarship from other sources will be reviewed while verifying the applications and the eligibility will be considered accordingly.\n"
        }
      ],
      "schemeDefinitions": [],
      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The student must be a domicile of the Sikkim state.\n   1. The student must belong to the Economically Weaker Section (EWS) as defined by the government.\n   1. The student must be enrolled in a recognized educational institution, a recognized distance education institution, or a recognized institution abroad. \n   1. The student should be studying in a registered coaching center.\n   1. A special consideration shall be given to students from marginalized, minority communities and specially abled categories (Divyangjan) and orphans.\n   1. The annual family income of the student shall not exceed a limit specified by the government, as revised from time to time.\n\n",
        "eligibilityDescription": [
          {
            "type": "align_justify",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "ol_list",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "list_item",
